Johnny Depp plays notorious Boston gangster James 'White' Bulger in the biopic Black Mass . 
  The first trailer for the film was released Thursday . 
  Bulger topped the FBI's most wanted list for 16 years before he was finally arrested in 2011 . 
  In the new trailer, Depp is completely transformed for the role . 
  The film is set to be released in September . 
 